// CallsLink
// Renders an orange clickable link for a cross-file function reference; shows a hover popover with file summary after a delay.
// synced: 2026-03-26T00:00:00Z

Constants: HOVER_DELAY = 400ms, GRACE_PERIOD = 300ms.
Two timers (hoverTimer, graceTimer) coordinate show/hide to prevent flickering when the cursor moves between the link and the popover.

FUNCTION CallsLink(name, fileStem, project, onNavigate) -> JSX.Element [2026-03-26]                EXPORT
  CALLS: fetchPseudoFile (pseudo-api), CallsPopover (CallsPopover)
  Manages popoverState { visible, anchorRect?, content? }.
  On mouse enter: clears any active grace timer, then after HOVER_DELAY fetches the file content via fetchPseudoFile and sets popoverState visible with the anchor's DOMRect and content. On fetch error, shows the popover with empty content.
  On mouse leave: clears the hover timer, then after GRACE_PERIOD sets popoverState to not visible.
  On click: clears both timers and calls onNavigate(fileStem).
  Popover mouse enter/leave handlers extend the grace period so the user can move the cursor into the popover without it dismissing.
  Renders a styled orange button showing "name (leafStem)". IF popoverState.visible, renders CallsPopover via portal.

---

FUNCTION clearHoverTimer() -> void
  Clears the hoverTimer ref if set and nulls it.

---

FUNCTION clearGraceTimer() -> void
  Clears the graceTimer ref if set and nulls it.

---

FUNCTION handleMouseEnter() -> void
  CALLS: fetchPseudoFile (pseudo-api)
  Clears grace timer, schedules popover display after HOVER_DELAY.

---

FUNCTION handleMouseLeave() -> void
  Clears hover timer, schedules popover hide after GRACE_PERIOD.

---

FUNCTION handleClick() -> void
  Clears both timers and calls onNavigate with fileStem.

---

FUNCTION handlePopoverMouseEnter() -> void
  Clears grace timer so popover stays visible while cursor is inside it.

---

FUNCTION handlePopoverMouseLeave() -> void
  Schedules popover hide after GRACE_PERIOD.
